00:07:43.072 --> 00:07:44.952
saying she wasn't worthy of you.

00:07:49.351 --> 00:07:50.431
Don't touch me.

00:07:51.472 --> 00:07:52.472
Your hands

00:07:52.671 --> 00:07:54.352
are still stained
with my mother's blood.

00:08:03.592 --> 00:08:05.071
Leave us.

00:08:07.952 --> 00:08:08.952
Qingru.

