for a strand of my mother's hair.

00:09:02.032 --> 00:09:04.192
This was left by your mother.

00:09:14.431 --> 00:09:15.712
I'd rather

00:09:16.191 --> 00:09:18.552
have been born to an ordinary family.

00:09:19.425 --> 00:09:20.620
At least then,

00:09:20.632 --> 00:09:23.472
I wouldn't have to endure
such hypocritical love.

